(109, 1, '2014-08-10 09:49:21', '2014-08-10 09:49:21', 'Business owners may have the option of cleaning their buildings themselves or hiring a commercial cleaning business to clean the building for them and many find that there are numerous benefits offered by hiring a commercial cleaning service for this work. Experience and reputation are the key things to look for in a commercial cleaning service.\r\n\r\nEnzymatic can clean anything and everything. We clean churches, office buildings, fitness centers, schools, restaurants, car repair shops, auto sales buildings, health care offices, stores and any other type of commercial building you have. By hiring us, you receive a huge benefit, and that is TIME. Getting our services will keep you free from completing the duties yourself. This means that you do not have to worry about how the building will get cleaned. When we are scheduled to come, we will show up and complete all of these duties for you.\r\n\r\nExperience and reputation – that is what sets us apart.', 'Commercial Cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-10 09:49:21', '2014-08-10 09:49:21', '', 12, 'http://localhost/enzymatic/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
